<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>Visual Comfort &amp; Co. — 8x8 Strategic Account Plan</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --dark: #2a2a2a;
    --darker: #1e1e1e;
    --teal: #00a99d;
    --lime: #bdd834;
    --orange: #f26522;
    --purple: #7b4f9e;
    --cream: #f5f0e8;
    --white: #ffffff;
    --text-dark: #1e1e1e;
    --text-mid: #444444;
    --text-light: #777777;
    --border: #e0d8cc;
    --success: #2ecc71;
    --warning: #f39c12;
    --danger: #e74c3c;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--text-dark);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    background: var(--darker);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 56px 64px 48px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -40px; right: -40px;
    width: 280px; height: 280px;
    background: var(--lime);
    clip-path: polygon(100% 0, 100% 100%, 0 0);
    opacity: 0.9;
  }
  .hero::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -20px; right: 160px;
    width: 120px; height: 120px;
    background: var(--teal);
    clip-path: polygon(50% 0%, 100% 100%, 0% 100%);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }
  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    border-radius: 30px;
    padding: 6px 16px;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 1.2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .hero-badge span { color: var(--lime); }
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 42px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }
  .hero h1 em { color: var(--lime); font-style: normal; }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }
  .hero-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 32px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }
  .hero-meta-item { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); }
  .hero-meta-item strong { display: block; color: var(--white); font-size: 14px; }

  /* ── POSTURE BANNER ── */
  .posture-banner {
    background: var(--teal);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 16px 64px;
    font-size: 14px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .posture-banner strong { font-size: 15px; }

  /* ── LAYOUT ── */
  .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 48px 64px; }
  .section { margin-bottom: 56px; }
  .section-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--teal);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--darker);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    padding-bottom: 12px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
  }

  /* ── STAT CARDS ── */
  .stat-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .stat-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px 18px;
    border-top: 4px solid var(--teal);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }
  .stat-card.orange { border-top-color: var(--orange); }
  .stat-card.lime { border-top-color: var(--lime); }
  .stat-card.purple { border-top-color: var(--purple); }
  .stat-card.dark { border-top-color: var(--darker); }
  .stat-number {
    font-size: 30px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--darker);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .stat-label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-light); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
  .stat-detail { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-mid); margin-top: 6px; }

  /* ── STAKEHOLDER CARDS ── */
  .stakeholder-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .stakeholder-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--border);
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .stakeholder-card.champion { border-left-color: var(--teal); }
  .stakeholder-card.executive { border-left-color: var(--orange); }
  .stakeholder-card.technical { border-left-color: var(--lime); }
  .stakeholder-card.partner { border-left-color: var(--purple); }
  .sk-role {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: var(--text-light);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .sk-name { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--darker); margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .sk-title { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-mid); margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .sk-email { font-size: 12px; color: var(--teal); text-decoration: none; }
  .sk-email:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .sk-priority {
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-mid);
    background: var(--cream);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 8px 10px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--lime);
  }
  .sk-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 6px;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.8px;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: var(--teal);
    color: var(--white);
  }

  /* ── LICENSE TABLE ── */
  .license-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; background: var(--white); border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); }
  .license-table th {
    background: var(--darker);
    color: var(--white);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.8px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .license-table td { padding: 11px 16px; font-size: 13px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .license-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  .license-table tr:hover td { background: #faf8f4; }
  .util-bar-wrap { width: 120px; height: 8px; background: #e8e3d8; border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; }
  .util-bar { height: 100%; border-radius: 4px; }
  .util-full { background: var(--orange); }
  .util-high { background: var(--warning); }
  .util-med { background: var(--teal); }
  .util-low { background: var(--border); }
  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .badge-red { background: #fde8e8; color: #c0392b; }
  .badge-yellow { background: #fef9e7; color: #b7770d; }
  .badge-teal { background: #e0f6f5; color: #007a74; }
  .badge-gray { background: #f0ece4; color: #666; }

  /* ── OPPORTUNITY CARDS ── */
  .opp-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 18px;
  }
  .opp-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 22px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }
  .opp-icon {
    font-size: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .opp-title { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--darker); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .opp-body { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-mid); line-height: 1.6; }
  .opp-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 12px;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 10px;
  }
  .tag-high { background: #fde8e8; color: #c0392b; }
  .tag-med { background: #fef3e2; color: #c17f24; }
  .tag-teal { background: #e0f6f5; color: #007a74; }

  /* ── RISK TABLE ── */
  .risk-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; background: var(--white); border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); }
  .risk-table th { background: var(--dark); color: var(--white); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.8px; padding: 12px 16px; text-align: left; }
  .risk-table td { padding: 12px 16px; font-size: 13px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); vertical-align: top; }
  .risk-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  .risk-dot { display: inline-block; width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; margin-right: 6px; vertical-align: middle; }
  .dot-high { background: var(--danger); }
  .dot-med { background: var(--warning); }

  /* ── TIMELINE ── */
  .timeline { position: relative; padding-left: 32px; }
  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 10px; top: 0; bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: var(--border);
  }
  .tl-item { position: relative; margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .tl-dot {
    position: absolute;
    left: -26px; top: 4px;
    width: 14px; height: 14px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--teal);
    border: 2px solid var(--white);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--teal);
  }
  .tl-dot.orange { background: var(--orange); box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--orange); }
  .tl-dot.lime { background: var(--lime); box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--lime); }
  .tl-date { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: var(--text-light); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .tl-content { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-dark); }
  .tl-content strong { color: var(--darker); }

  /* ── ROADMAP ── */
  .roadmap { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 16px; }
  .roadmap-phase {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 22px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }
  .roadmap-phase.phase1 { border-top: 4px solid var(--teal); }
  .roadmap-phase.phase2 { border-top: 4px solid var(--orange); }
  .roadmap-phase.phase3 { border-top: 4px solid var(--lime); }
  .phase-label {
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .phase1 .phase-label { color: var(--teal); }
  .phase2 .phase-label { color: var(--orange); }
  .phase3 .phase-label { color: #7a8c00; }
  .phase-title { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--darker); margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .phase-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-mid);
  }
  .phase-item::before {
    content: '→';
    color: var(--teal);
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 1px;
  }

  /* ── METRICS TABLE ── */
  .metrics-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .metric-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    border-bottom: 3px solid var(--border);
  }
  .metric-card.teal { border-bottom-color: var(--teal); }
  .metric-card.orange { border-bottom-color: var(--orange); }
  .metric-card.lime { border-bottom-color: var(--lime); }
  .metric-outcome { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.8px; color: var(--text-light); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .metric-kpi { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-dark); }

  /* ── ACTIVE INITIATIVES ── */
  .initiative-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; }
  .initiative-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 18px 22px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    border-left: 5px solid var(--teal);
  }
  .initiative-card.orange { border-left-color: var(--orange); }
  .initiative-card.purple { border-left-color: var(--purple); }
  .initiative-card.warning { border-left-color: var(--warning); }
  .init-icon { font-size: 22px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }
  .init-title { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--darker); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .init-body { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-mid); }
  .init-status {
    margin-left: auto;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.8px;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    align-self: center;
  }
  .status-active { background: #e0f6f5; color: #007a74; }
  .status-pending { background: #fef3e2; color: #c17f24; }
  .status-paused { background: #fde8e8; color: #c0392b; }
  .status-monitor { background: #f0ece4; color: #666; }

  /* ── TEAM GRID ── */
  .team-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .team-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 18px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .team-avatar {
    width: 48px; height: 48px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--darker);
    color: var(--white);
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 10px;
  }
  .team-avatar.teal { background: var(--teal); }
  .team-avatar.orange { background: var(--orange); }
  .team-avatar.purple { background: var(--purple); }
  .team-name { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--darker); }
  .team-role { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-light); margin-top: 2px; }
  .team-email { font-size: 11px; color: var(--teal); margin-top: 4px; text-decoration: none; }
  .team-email:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  /* ── NARRATIVE BOX ── */
  .narrative-box {
    background: var(--darker);
    color: var(--white);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 32px 36px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .narrative-box::before {
    content: '"';
    position: absolute;
    top: -10px; left: 20px;
    font-size: 120px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    line-height: 1;
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
  }
  .narrative-box p {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
  }
  .narrative-box strong { color: var(--lime); }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  .footer {
    background: var(--darker);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    padding: 24px 64px;
    font-size: 12px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .footer strong { color: var(--white); }

  /* ── PRINT / RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero { padding: 36px 24px; }
    .container { padding: 32px 24px; }
    .posture-banner { padding: 14px 24px; }
    .footer { padding: 18px 24px; }
    .roadmap { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 30px; }
  }
  @media print {
    body { background: white; }
    .hero { print-color-adjust: exact; -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact; }
  }

  /* ── DIVIDER ── */
  .divider { height: 1px; background: var(--border); margin: 0 0 48px; }

  /* ── TWO-COL ── */
  .two-col { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .info-box {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  }
  .info-box h4 { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.8px; color: var(--text-light); margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .info-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); font-size: 13px; }
  .info-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .info-row span:first-child { color: var(--text-mid); }
  .info-row span:last-child { font-weight: 600; color: var(--darker); }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-badge"><span>●</span> Active Enterprise Account</div>
  <h1>Visual Comfort &amp; Co.<br><em>Strategic Account Plan</em></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">8x8 UCaaS + CCaaS | Enterprise | Houston, TX &amp; UK</p>
  <div class="hero-meta">
    <div class="hero-meta-item"><strong>Mark Davenport</strong>Enterprise AE — 8x8</div>
    <div class="hero-meta-item"><strong>Geoff Stoddart</strong>Senior CSM — 8x8</div>
    <div class="hero-meta-item"><strong>Mike Foreman</strong>Solutions Engineer</div>
    <div class="hero-meta-item"><strong>Last Updated</strong>July 23, 2026</div>
    <div class="hero-meta-item"><strong>QBR Scheduled</strong>July 28, 2026</div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- POSTURE BANNER -->
<div class="posture-banner">
  <strong>Strategic Posture:</strong> Protect the core platform → Support the customer's chosen AI strategy (Avoca + ElevenLabs) → Expand through Salesforce, QM, WFM, digital engagement, and proactive outreach.
</div>

<div class="container">

  <!-- ACCOUNT SNAPSHOT -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">Account Overview</div>
    <div class="section-title">Account at a Glance</div>

    <div class="stat-grid">
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-number">8+ yrs</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Partnership Tenure</div>
        <div class="stat-detail">Customer since March 2018</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card orange">
        <div class="stat-number">~1,440</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Total 8x8 Users</div>
        <div class="stat-detail">925 named user entitlements active</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card lime">
        <div class="stat-number">78</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Deployed Sites</div>
        <div class="stat-detail">US + United Kingdom</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card purple">
        <div class="stat-number">185</div>
        <div class="stat-label">CC Agents</div>
        <div class="stat-detail">Contact Center Advanced — 100% assigned</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card dark">
        <div class="stat-number">3</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Active SOWs / Projects</div>
        <div class="stat-detail">AvocaAI PS, SIP Trunk, BYAI ElevenLabs</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="two-col">
      <div class="info-box">
        <h4>Technology Stack</h4>
        <div class="info-row"><span>Enterprise Telephony</span><span>8x8 ✓</span></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span>Contact Center</span><span>8x8 CC Advanced ✓</span></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span>Collaboration &amp; Video</span><span>Microsoft Teams</span></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span>WFM (Hive65)</span><span>8x8 WFM ✓ (Top-15 User)</span></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span>CRM</span><span>Migrating Zendesk → Salesforce</span></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span>AI IVR / Voice Agent</span><span>Avoca AI + ElevenLabs TTS</span></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span>SIP Trunk for AI</span><span>8x8 (O-214411) — In Progress</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="info-box">
        <h4>CX Performance Baseline (July 2025 EBR)</h4>
        <div class="info-row"><span>Call Acceptance Rate</span><span style="color:var(--teal);font-weight:700;">97%</span></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span>Avg Wait Time</span><span style="color:var(--teal);font-weight:700;">13 seconds</span></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span>Known Strength</span><span>Knowledgeable staff</span></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span>Improvement Area</span><span>IVR messaging &amp; scripts</span></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span>Improvement Area</span><span>Post-call survey participation</span></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span>Improvement Area</span><span>Known-customer data utilization</span></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span>Next Validation</span><span>After Avoca launch</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CUSTOMER PROFILE -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-label">Customer Context</div>
    <div class="section-title">About Visual Comfort &amp; Co.</div>
    <div class="narrative-box" style="margin-bottom:24px;">
      <p>Visual Comfort &amp; Co. is a premium decorative and architectural lighting company serving consumers, designers, architects, builders, contractors, trade professionals, and wholesale partners. Their brand promise — <strong>original design, premium materials, craftsmanship</strong> — demands that every customer touchpoint, from the showroom floor to the contact center, matches that standard. Communications isn't an IT function at Visual Comfort; it's part of the brand experience.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="two-col">
      <div class="info-box">
        <h4>Why Communications Matters Here</h4>
        <div class="info-row"><span>Complex buying journeys</span><span>Orders, specs, warranty, install</span></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span>Multiple buyer personas</span><span>Consumer, designer, trade, B2B</span></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span>Premium brand standard</span><span>Service must match product quality</span></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span>Distributed workforce</span><span>78 sites incl. showrooms &amp; design offices</span></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span>Seasonal complexity</span><span>Demand spikes around collections &amp; launches</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="info-box">
        <h4>Key Customer Objectives</h4>
        <div class="info-row"><span>AI-driven self-service</span><span>Avoca + ElevenLabs POC</span></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span>CRM unification</span><span>Salesforce replacing Zendesk</span></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span>WFM optimization</span><span>Hive65 rollout (breaks/schedule bug active)</span></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span>Agent quality</span><span>QM fully licensed — adoption TBD</span></div>
        <div class="info-row"><span>Executive CX vision</span><span>Miti Desai leading transformation</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

