      <div class="opp-card">
        <div class="opp-icon">🔗</div>
        <div class="opp-title">Salesforce Integration</div>
        <div class="opp-body">Zendesk → Salesforce migration is the #1 CRM priority. 8x8's native Salesforce connector delivers screen pops, auto-logging, AI summaries, case creation, and routing based on CRM data. Embedding communications into Salesforce gives Miti Desai the unified customer view she needs. ElevenLabs and Avoca AI are already in the ElevenLabs | Salesforce &amp; 8x8 Kickoff thread.</div>
        <span class="opp-tag tag-high">High Priority</span>
      </div>

      <div class="opp-card">
        <div class="opp-icon">📊</div>
        <div class="opp-title">QM &amp; Speech Analytics Activation</div>
        <div class="opp-body">All 185 QM licenses are assigned — but are they fully used? Confirm adoption of evaluation forms, coaching workflows, calibration, screen recording, and speech-driven scoring. Key use case: compare Avoca-handled vs. transferred vs. agent-only journeys to quantify AI ROI. Visual Comfort is already flagged as a top-15 WFM user, suggesting data-driven adoption.</div>
        <span class="opp-tag tag-high">High Priority</span>
      </div>

      <div class="opp-card">
        <div class="opp-icon">📅</div>
        <div class="opp-title">WFM Optimization (Hive65)</div>
        <div class="opp-body">Visual Comfort is a <strong>top-15 WFM user</strong> (per Jonathan McKenzie email July 23). Active issues with Hive65 breaks-disappearing bug need resolution. Opportunity: model how Avoca AI containment changes staffing needs, optimize schedules around seasonal lighting launches, showroom hours, and trade-program activity. WFM is a stickiness and expansion play.</div>
        <span class="opp-tag tag-med">Medium Priority</span>
      </div>

      <div class="opp-card">
        <div class="opp-icon">💬</div>
        <div class="opp-title">Digital Engagement</div>
        <div class="opp-body">Web chat, messaging, appointment scheduling for showroom and virtual design consultations. Premium brand customers expect digital escalation from AI → live agent. Glenda Martinez (Design Director) is already engaged in the kickoff thread — design consultation, product image sharing, and video support are natural fits for the Visual Comfort premium experience.</div>
        <span class="opp-tag tag-med">Medium Priority</span>
      </div>

      <div class="opp-card">
        <div class="opp-icon">📣</div>
        <div class="opp-title">Proactive Outreach</div>
        <div class="opp-body">Outbound notifications for order status, delivery, backorder, appointment reminders, warranty follow-up, showroom event invites, and collection launches. Reduces inbound call volume and aligns with Avoca AI containment goals. Especially valuable for the designer/trade segment and seasonal spikes.</div>
        <span class="opp-tag tag-teal">Near Term</span>
      </div>

