    <div class="section-title">How We Tell the 8x8 Story</div>
    <div class="narrative-box">
      <p>Visual Comfort has chosen <strong>Avoca AI and ElevenLabs</strong> for their voice-agent strategy, and 8x8 should help make that decision successful. Our role is to provide the <strong>reliable communications, contact-center, quality management, workforce optimization, CRM integration, and customer-interaction foundation</strong> around the AI experience. By connecting Avoca, ElevenLabs, 8x8, Salesforce, and Visual Comfort's human service teams, we help create <strong>one measurable, premium customer journey</strong> — rather than another isolated technology deployment. We are not just the phone system. We are the platform that makes every other investment work.</p>
